Subject: [PATCH] meson: link D-Bus independently of PipeWire features

kde_night_light.c is always compiled and uses libdbus directly. Keep D-Bus in
the base dependency list so builds with both PipeWire features disabled work.

--- a/meson.build
+++ b/meson.build
@@ -76,0 +77 @@
+    dependency('dbus-1'),
@@ -109 +109,0 @@
-        dependency('dbus-1'),
